Indonesia's Mount Sinabung erupts, killing at least six people in Sumatra. (AFP via ABC News Australia)An Aerogaviota-operated Antonov An-26 plane crashes in western Artemisa Province, Cuba, killing eight troops on board. (Daily Mail) (AP via Miami Herald)An avalanche on Mount Nasu in Japan's Tochigi Prefecture, kills at least eight schoolchildren while the students were on a mountaineering excursion. There are three students and three teachers missing. (AFP via Channel News Asia), (CNN)